snippet.title: NASCAR 99 - PS1 Gameplay (1080p60fps)
snippet.description:
NASCAR 99 - PlayStation 1 Gameplay (1080p60fps).

NASCAR 99 is a racing simulator video game developed and published by EA Sports and co-developed by Stormfront Studios. It was released for Nintendo 64 on September 11, 1998, and for the PlayStation on September 28, 1998. NASCAR 99 was the second game in the EA Sports NASCAR series of video games.
